7.What module contains Pillow’s shape-drawing code?

Ans: Pillow's shape-drawing code is found in the "ImageDraw" module. This module provides a drawing interface for creating and manipulating images.
It allows users to draw various shapes, lines, and text on images, providing a versatile set of tools
for image processing and graphical applications within the Pillow library.

